name: complex_arith_negated_sum_equals_sum_of_negations
section: arithmetic-normalization
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Negating a three-term sum should equal summing the individual negations.
law: (= (fuzz-sub 0 (fuzz-add {a} (fuzz-add {b} {c}))) (fuzz-add (fuzz-sub 0 {a}) (fuzz-add (fuzz-sub 0 {b}) (fuzz-sub 0 {c}))))
